cc:Work.dc:title: Caveman with Axe and Torch
cc:Work.dc:description: This is George. He is off to work at the office. Wait. Nooooo! That ain't right. This is a stereotypical "caveman" synthesized from a super old (thus public domain) book cover about natural history. I wonder why he has such a huge beard but no chest hair. He has weird genetics, eh.
